Hmmm.... I know I'm gonna get it, but here goes...

I stopped using clamps on the axle end of my CV boots many years ago. I
found that the boots lasted much longer, and I haven't had noticeable wear
on the joints. Driving through deep water warrants an inspection, though. Go
ahead and clean them out as you described, and let us know what you find.

